# Task Exec Agent

When the user asks to implement a task, execute a task spec, or verify task completion:

1. Read [.ai/agents/task-exec.md](.ai/agents/task-exec.md)
2. Read the task spec in `docs/task-specs/` and exec plan in `docs/task-exec-plans/active/`
3. Implement following layer order and project patterns
4. Run only the **Verification** checks from the task spec (subset of full test suite)
5. On success: update checkboxes, move to completed, update [docs/TASKS.md](docs/TASKS.md)
